Description: Speech-first inference runtime (shared library + C header)
 Vokra is an ONNX Runtime alternative specialised for speech AI (TTS / ASR /
 speech-to-speech / VAD). This package ships the C ABI shared library
 (libvokra.so) and the header (vokra.h). Zero external runtime dependencies.
